        rdfs:comment        "A low level of RAC1 activity is essential to maintain axon outgrowth. ROBO activation recruits SOS, a dual specificity GEF, to the plasma membrane via Dock homolog NCK (NCK1 or NCK2) to activate RAC1 during midline repulsion." ;
